comments.body:
[~ywskycn], we shouldn't use /tmp as that does not get clean up by the build, instead we should use a temp subdir under target/, easily done by:

{code}
File dir = new File("target", UUID.randomUUID());
dir.mkdirs();
{code}

And the documentation, in the appendix should have a complete/simple example of an sls JSON input file as a reference.

